174,"uid":124114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:01:45.000Z","msg":"試過食,但真係食唔落,完全唔明有咩好食<br />\n酒都係,苦o既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,不過涼瓜我都會食"},{"pid":"bb85f3c260426b01c2451631bc62efb1a748ad3a","tid":554174,"uid":141419,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:08:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老一輩就算啦食咗幾十年<br />\n<br />\n但係年輕個代絕大部份都接受過教育<br />\n<br />\n食煙嘅禍害應該大家都知嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n我諗唔明點解仲會有後生去食<br />\n<br />\n明知有害都仲要食 唉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老一輩就算啦做咗幾十年<br />\n<br />\n但係年輕個代絕大部份都接受過教育<br />\n<br />\n賣命嘅禍害應該大家都知嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n我諗唔明點解仲會有後生去幫人打工<br />\n<br />\n明知對自己有害都仲要做 唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n煙同酒，可能係活係繁囂都市嘅各位一個放鬆媒介。（唔探討煙點黎）<br />\n冇得簡命運嘅好壞，只求一刻嘅自我放縱<br />\n<br />\n利申：冇食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會憎人食煙，但好憎俾人噴到成面煙"},{"pid":"a7a1d82be8d7063c01288dee71074d4bca20b3c0","tid":554174,"uid":153250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:16:56.000Z","msg":"有時好多野煩同攰都會想點返枝煙放鬆下既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申有食/我都好憎火車頭"},{"pid":"3609c53d1495ebedbc7a6de972042279b26618b2","tid":554174,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e401bd9a80ce30795466dac5bf45fb60f353cadc","tid":554174,"uid":80719,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T09:36:39.000Z","msg":"食煙先醒，人類唔洗咁長命，何況中共遲早拎番香港，快d玩完冇眼屎乾淨盲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:20:45.000Z","msg":"食煙係有眼屎焦油盲"},{"pid":"736659cdbbb660896875f3402dd61c64ab65cdf4","tid":554174,"uid":78349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:22:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地話為咗合群<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要靠呢啲不良嗜好先合到既群 唔合都罷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8af3d27fdc3f2d6aab23d44c922a1cb7a1c30d8","